column5: wow 2 of april and i have a sunburn and muusquito bites crazy what a great day

Archer I know what ya mean. i have been fishin the past 3 days.. and my arms look like tomatoes!  and then on top of that when i go in back bays for crappie.. I come out lookin like I got friggin chicken pox! lol but hey Im not complaining!
ps you better be out there getting team 10 some points !
I thought I was the only bugger around who got a sun burn(Half my face and the arm I have out the tucks window) haha And a few bug bites aswelL!

i brought the boat home yesterday. Just finished installing the new trolling motor the old floor is out cut the new wood today and wait or the carpet to get here and then with a bit o luck on to the water in 2 weeks
ugh... Fine.. i guess I'll take it upon myself to start catching fish.. jeez...!
don't blame me the carpet was to be here last thrus
haha well hope it comes soon. but hey atleast you dont have to sit out the warm days.. next weeks supose to rain a bit so.. get'r done and we'll cya on the water!
